<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Bookipedia</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 m-auto">
          <h1 class="text-center display-4 my-4">Bookipedia Files Upload</h1>
          <form action="/upload" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <div class="custom-file mb-3">
              <input
                type="file"
                name="file"
                id="file"
                class="custom-file-input"
              />
              <label for="file" class="custom-file-label">Choose File</label>
            </div>
            <input
              type="submit"
              value="Submit"
              class="btn btn-primary btn-block"
            />
          </form>
          <hr />
          <p>Get pdf files from url: 
            <a href="https://bookipedia-files.vercel.app/fileinfo/">https://bookipedia-files.vercel.app/fileinfo/[file_id]</a>
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Don't forget to replace [file_id] with the actual id
            </li>
            <li>
              When upload file this will be an `id` returned 
              in the json response use it to get the file in the above url
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p> ðŸš© note: vercel doesn't allow more than 6mb payload, 
                so don't uplaod or download more than about 4mb file in one request,
                until we have some mony to move to something else, 
                and configure the file streaming rate.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
